parameters: \N<Yuia>How much time has passed since then...?

\N<Yuia>How long has it been since I was shoved into a place like
this...?
\N<Yuia>Damn it...! This isn't the time to be doing this...!
\N<Male Voice>Hehehe, hurry along now. Your beloved husband is just ahead.
\N<Woman'S Voice>He is... in a place like this...
\N<Segi>Yes... Lord Yuia. It's me. I've come to see you...

\N<Zuuteruka>Hehehe, Yuia. How do you like living here? Have you taken a
liking to it even a little?
\N<Yuia>Zuuteruka...! Are you there too!? What are you doing here!?

\N<Zuuteruka>What am I doing here? I went out of my way to escort your
lovely wife all the way down to this dungeon, and this is
how you speak to me?
\N<Yuia>Don't mess with me!! Let me out of here!!

\N<Segi>Lord Yuia... both the child and I are fine. I'm sorry for
making you worry...

\N<Segi>But please, just a little longer... be patient. Everything
will surely work out...
\N<Yuia>What are you talking about, it's not your fault...!
\N<Segi>I'm, I'm fine... everything will surely work out.
